                <div style="flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:36px 14px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
                    <span style="color:#94A3B8;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;">←</span>
                    <p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">Submit Stream Recap</p>
                  </div>
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;">
                    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;"><div style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:#7C3AED;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><span style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:white;">1</span></div><span style="font-size:9px;color:#94A3B8;">Platform</span></div>
                    <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:#7C3AED;margin-bottom:14px;"></div>
                    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;"><div style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:#7C3AED;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><span style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:white;">2</span></div><span style="font-size:9px;color:#94A3B8;">Upload</span></div>
                    <div style="flex:1;height:1px;background:#2A2040;margin-bottom:14px;"></div>
                    <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:3px;"><div style="width:22px;height:22px;border-radius:50%;background:#2A2040;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;"><span style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#64748B;">3</span></div><span style="font-size:9px;color:#64748B;">Analyze</span></div>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">WHERE DID YOU STREAM?</p>
                  <div style="display:flex;gap:7px;">
                    <span style="background:rgba(124,58,237,0.2);border:1.5px solid #7C3AED;color:#A78BFA;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:20px;">● Twitch</span>
                    <span style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;color:#64748B;font-size:11px;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:20px;">● YouTube</span>
                    <span style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;color:#64748B;font-size:11px;padding:5px 11px;border-radius:20px;">● TikTok</span>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">ANALYTICS SCREENSHOT</p>
                  <div style="border:1.5px dashed #2A2040;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 14px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:#100D1C;">
                    <svg width="28" height="28" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="1.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg>
                    <p style="font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;">Drop your screenshot here</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#4A4A6A;margin:0;">or tap to browse from Photos</p>
                    <p style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;margin:0;">PNG, JPG · Max 10MB</p>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#64748B;margin:0;">WHAT TO SCREENSHOT</p>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;">
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">📊 Channel analytics summary (peak viewers, avg viewers, hours)</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">👥 Follower/subscriber growth chart for the session</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">💬 Chat activity or engagement metrics</p>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background:#141028;border:1px solid #2A2040;border-radius:10px;padding:11px;text-align:center;">
                    <span style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#4A4A6A;">Upload a screenshot first</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div style="flex-shrink:0;height:54px;background:#06040F;border-top:1px solid #2A2040;display:flex;align-items:center;">
                  <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 12L12 3l9 9M5 10v9a1 1 0 001 1h4v-5h4v5h4a1 1 0 001-1v-9"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Home</span></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#7C3AED" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-4M17 8l-5-5-5 5M12 3v12"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#7C3AED;font-weight:600;">Upload</span></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Analysis</span></div>
                  <div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:2px;"><svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" stroke="#4A4A6A" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="4"/><path d="M6 20v-2a4 4 0 014-4h4a4 4 0 014 4v2"/></svg><span style="font-size:9px;color:#4A4A6A;">Progress</span></div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- ── Screen 2: Analysis ── -->
              <div class="sl-screen" data-screen="2" style="position:absolute;inset:0;display:none;flex-direction:column;background:#080614;">
                <div style="flex:1;overflow-y:auto;padding:36px 14px 10px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;">
                  <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;">
                    <span style="color:#94A3B8;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;">←</span>
                    <p style="font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">Stream Analysis</p>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:10px;color:#64748B;margin:0;letter-spacing:0.5px;">WEEK 3 · TWITCH · NOV 12</p>
                  <h3 style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;line-height:1.3;">Playing Hollow Knight — First Playthrough</h3>
                  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:6px;">
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">8</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">peak viewers</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">3.2</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">avg viewers</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">1h47</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">duration</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:8px 4px;text-align:center;"><p style="font-size:16px;font-weight:700;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0;">+2</p><p style="font-size:8px;color:#64748B;margin:2px 0 0;line-height:1.2;">followers</p></div>
                  </div>
                  <div style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.1);border:1px solid rgba(34,197,94,0.3);border-radius:10px;padding:10px 12px;">
                    <p style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#22C55E;margin:0 0 4px;">CHALLENGE COMPLETE ✓</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;color:#86EFAC;margin:0;line-height:1.5;">You streamed for 71 minutes without checking. You nailed it.</p>
                    <p style="font-size:10px;font-weight:700;color:#22C55E;margin:4px 0 0;">+150 XP earned</p>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#22C55E;margin:0;">✓ WHAT WENT WELL</p>
                  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;"><p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0 0 3px;">You held your audience</p><p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Average viewer retention was 40% — solid for your stage.</p></div>
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;"><p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0 0 3px;">Natural reactions</p><p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">Peak moment (8 viewers) came during the boss fight.</p></div>
                  </div>
                  <p style="font-size:9px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;color:#F97316;margin:0;">⚠ WHAT TO WORK ON</p>
                  <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;">
                    <div style="background:#141028;border-radius:8px;padding:9px 11px;"><p style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:#F1F5F9;margin:0 0 3px;">Dead air at the start</p><p style="font-size:10px;color:#94A3B8;margin:0;line-height:1.4;">You lost 2 viewers in the first 8 minutes — talk constantly during loading.</p></div>
